                "invention-title": [
                    "Zero-carbon method for preparing sponge iron from red mud",
                    "一种赤泥零碳制备海绵铁的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a zero-carbon method for preparing sponge iron from red mud, which comprises the following steps of: performing low-temperature fluidized solid-state reduction on iron oxide in the red mud to metal iron by taking hydrogen as a reducing agent and fluidizing gas, and performing magnetic separation to obtain high-activity sponge iron with the metallization ratio of more than or equal to 90 percent; hydrogen combustion is adopted to provide heat required by the system, a combustion product is only water vapor, and zero carbon emission of the system is achieved; a high-rotating-speed gas-solid stirring fluidized bed with a built-in bottom stretching type multi-layer stirring paddle is adopted, and efficient drying, dehydration, scattering and conveying of the red mud are achieved. And the energy utilization rate of the system is improved through heat exchange between cold hydrogen and hot reduction materials. The process equipment is simple, the operation is simple and convenient, the energy consumption is low, the high-moisture and high-viscosity red mud can be treated, the raw material application range is wide, the carbon emission is zero, the environment-friendly effect is realized, the high-activity sponge iron can be cleanly and efficiently prepared from the red mud on a large scale, and the economic benefit and the social benefit are good."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种赤泥零碳制备海绵铁的方法，以氢气为还原剂和流化气，低温流态化固态还原赤泥中的氧化铁至金属铁，磁选得到高活性海绵铁，海绵铁的金属化率≥90％；采用氢气燃烧提供系统所需热量，燃烧产物只有水蒸气，实现系统零碳排放；采用内置底伸式多层搅拌桨的高转速气固搅拌流化床，实现对赤泥的高效干燥、脱水、打散和输送；通过冷氢气与热还原料换热，提高系统能量利用率。本发明工艺设备简单，操作简便，能耗低，可处理高水分、高粘度赤泥料，原料适用范围广，零碳排放，环境友好，可以实现赤泥大规模清洁高效制备高活性海绵铁，具有良好的经济效益和社会效益。"
                }
            ]
